        <section class="section helping-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="section-heading sc-section-heading">
                        <h3>We Need Your Help</h3>
                        <p>Mission Fuel was started by regular people just like you who through short term missions projects were moved to action by the love of Christ for the people who they encountered. Having exceeded our own financial resources to provide the assistance needed, we are now reaching out to others who would like to join our work. </p> 
